    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped to Gradation 1 and not assessed per MRL 2 guidance. Validation results demonstrate CFD predictions of relative hemolysis index within acceptance criteria across all 5 CPB operating points. A screening sensitivity study performed during model development confirmed rotational speed as the dominant driver of hemolysis index, supporting the operating envelope selection. The model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device under the stated COU.",
